{"tid":1426870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影啦影啦 依家影出禍啦","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:00:18.000Z","uid":24930,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b56cd5bea9e9da80061eaded6ae97eb4de574f9b","tid":1426870,"uid":24930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"想講<br />\n見唔見到依幾日有幾咁多人需要拍片影相支援<br />\n「邊到邊到幾點鐘有冇人拍到片！急需片段！」<br />\n其實拍片影相 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">係無問題</span></strong></span><br />\n問題只係在於你點運用呢d片段/相<br />\n影到人大頭既 唔好po上社交媒體啦拜託<br />\n社運唔係比你用黎打卡既地方<br />\n如果因為你既打卡而令手足被拉<br />\n你過唔撚過意得去<br />\n有目的地去影低環境比frd睇又另計<br />\n影定用黎做證據用黎幫人<br />\n就更加要<br />\n講到口臭都要講<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班撚樣咪再一見人舉機就屌柒人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">提醒手足唔好影大頭唔好亂po上網就夠</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw標題黨 sorry呃左你入黎 多謝你睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b285d0fb7cf22db9d66a6e833ae379e3ec4f5b","tid":1426870,"uid":24930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"禮貌少少你班撚樣 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5b1224238ac3b62fc78cd8896e0191549f9675","tid":1426870,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc19732b0a60fb819588edd80c10d28f47773a92","tid":1426870,"uid":22063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"講啲啱 <br />\n唔可以一概唔俾人影<br />\n大家提高警覺，適當地保護自己就得"},{"pid":"b8a9fc7987b464bb9b71692720f4de18ecfcbb17","tid":1426870,"uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b56c